li.font: A Thing (e.g. a weather station) aggregates the measurements from sensors
A Thing sends them to a SensorThings API endpoint in DataHubHel
DataHubHel checks that the Thing is registered
DataHubHel sends the data forward to the STS
DataHubHel receives data from STS via MQTT and sends the data into the public MQTT Broker
Services subscribe to Datastreams via MQTT
